{"tid":2441133,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果自殺重新成為刑事罪行，咪可以解決自殺問題囉？","createTime":"2021-03-10T12:39:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T12:42:11.000Z","uid":290404,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"72865a75895b361a78c2ca89455fdd804fb974c3","tid":2441133,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T12:39:28.000Z","msg":"以前係香港，自殺的確係刑事罪行，直到1961年因為英國廢除自殺罪，先至同步廢除。<br />\n但目前有D國家仍然將自殺納入刑事罪行，星馬地區不時都有人因為自殺被送上法庭定罪，判罰款甚至坐監。<br />\n如果自殺同偷野、吸毒一樣，都係刑事罪行，咪可以阻嚇D想自殺既人囉！<br />\n好似港大社工系教授葉兆輝之前都有提議過架！點解唔考慮重新將自殺訂為刑事罪行？"},{"pid":"11c5a295169a3794321436d5c47d17d6f8d33aea","tid":2441133,"uid":2419,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T12:41:30.000Z","msg":"判死刑 嚇死佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b033dbef92b9e7e8ab10cbe84918e247a56494af","tid":2441133,"uid":290404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"11c5a295169a3794321436d5c47d17d6f8d33aea","tid":2441133,"uid":2419,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T12:41:30.000Z","msg":"判死刑 嚇死佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T12:42:09.000Z","msg":"求仁得仁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f9bfa78d516af1012292f68863b1c6029cf50f","tid":2441133,"uid":367147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T12:44:04.000Z","msg":"咁樣根本解決唔到問題<br />\n反而死嗰啲會更徹底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff16d36876abc7df8fa8e924351974e54abf592b","tid":2441133,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T12:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdb43dedf4953c1e1b19733344979c8799c79763","tid":2441133,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"57f9bfa78d516af1012292f68863b1c6029cf50f","tid":2441133,"uid":367147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,